* 2. Issues *

- only volume by volume backup is supported
- so far only nwfs and local mount are supported
- you must append 'ago' to delete_after options
- no man page

* 3. How to Install *

 1. run ./install
 2. read TUTORIAL
 3. modify the example configuration file to your needs
 4. set up the environment
 5. try it out!

* 4. Misc. *

Have a lot of fun!

